  "aboutContent": "<a style='font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center;'><img src='snail.png' style='width: 100px;'>&nbsp;Snail Note 2.0</a><br><a style='font-size:14px; display: flex; text-align: justify; margin-top: -10px; padding-right: 5px;'>This is a productive and simple code editor programme for convenient work without an overloaded interface and unnecessary features. At any time, you can install extensions and themes, customising everything to your taste. The application is built on ElectronJS. Syntax highlighting is supported thanks to Monaco Editor (by Microsoft), with plans to transition to a custom syntax highlighting engine in the future. For convenient work with folders, there is an explorer on the left side of the screen, which allows easy navigation in large projects. Thank you for choosing Snail Code :3 <br><br>By the way, why a snail? As a child, I used to take snails from the street, and they lived in little houses at my place.</a><br><a style='color: #007acc !important; display: flex; align-items: center; font-size: 14px;' href='https://github.com/bebka16/note' target='new'><img src='git.webp' style='width: 30px; margin-right: 5px;'>GitHub project page and source code </a><br><a style='margin-top: -10px; color: #007acc !important; display: flex; align-items: center; font-size: 14px;' href='https://bebkalive.t.me' target='new'><img src='tg.png' style='width: 30px; margin-right: 5px;'>Developer's Telegram channel</a>         <br><a style='margin-top: -10px; color: #007acc !important; display: flex; align-items: center; font-size: 14px;' href='https://bebka16.github.io/note/docs.html' target='new'><img src='dc.png' style='width: 30px; margin-right: 5px;'>Programme documentation</a>            <br><a style='margin-top: -10px; color: #007acc !important; display: flex; align-items: center; font-size: 14px;' href='https://bebka16.github.io' target='new'><img src='site.png' style='width: 30px; margin-right: 5px;'>Developer's official website</a>            <br><a style='margin-top: -10px; clor: #007acc !important; display: flex; align-items: center; font-size: 14px;'  target='new'>Your programme version: 2.0.0.</a><br><br><a style='margin-top: -10px; clor: #007acc !important; display: flex; align-items: center; font-size: 14px;'  target='new'>&copy bebka16, 2022 — 2026. All rights reserved. You have the right to view the code, use its parts in your projects, but the authorship of this programme remains with me.</a>",
